接口 IClosableIterator<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - The type being iterated over
    所有超级接口:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, java.util.Iterator<T>
    所有已知实现类:
    Cursor, EmptyClosableIterator

    public interface IClosableIterator<T>
extends java.util.Iterator<T>, java.io.Closeable
    An iterator that must be closed after use
